				<td colspan="2"><span>It's a great song.  It gates the mob, dispells them once and
<br />
interrupts casting.  It does cause agro.  It can be resisted and
<br />
I don't know of a level cap on it.  I've gated a lvl 60 mob
<br />
before.  You can cause some wicked trains with this.  Don't
<br />
do it in a zone where you could agro a DT mob... heh.
<br />

<br />
I used it to single out pulls before, to find the PH for Eldrig the
<br />
old and just as a general time buyer.</span></td>
