				<td colspan="2"><span>Thanks! I'm one yellow (20%) to 56 now after FINALLY completing Baron last night (I procrastinate), so I wanted to get around to finding out about this song.
<br />

<br />
Velvett, without jinxing (sp) anything, the concept is to gate a mob to it's spawn point with Highsun and then hit fading memories (agro wipe essentially) and the mob forgets you.  It is used quite effectively for pulling if you get multiples, just send them home and turn on the TV so they become mindless couch potatoes again... 
<br />

<br />
Sounds like a useful song, I could see this on our next fear raid if we are going to wipe, it can get a cleric and maybe a few more camped before they can train the entire zone and CT on top of us.  Not sure it's a big enough zone to do that but may be worth a try in a pinch.
<br />

<br />
Thanks again,
<br />

