				<td colspan="2"><span>Take this for example.  Your running along PoD and you see
<br />
a named fly up on tracking.  So you run over there and agro
<br />
the whole island of flies. Then you run the back to a safe kite
<br />
spot and begin to gate the adds back 1 by 1.   After the last
<br />
one is gone you hit that AA from PoP called Fading Memories.
<br />
Now you can simply kill the named mob and not worry about
<br />
the adds.
<br />

<br />
Apply that to higher level PoP content and it really starts to
<br />
get good heh.  Not to mention it's an absolute train stopper.
